00:00:08.225 --> 00:00:10.727 line:90%
<i>Princess!</i>

00:00:22.072 --> 00:00:23.740 line:90%
Does it torment you

00:00:23.824 --> 00:00:26.868 line:90%
to know of the bloodshed
your family caused 30 years ago?

00:00:26.952 --> 00:00:30.831 line:90%
Do you despise your parents so deeply
that you offer your body to a spirit?

00:00:32.332 --> 00:00:34.125 line:90%
<i>Your mother came to see me.</i>

00:00:34.209 --> 00:00:36.461 line:90%
She pleaded with me to save her daughter.

00:00:47.556 --> 00:00:50.976 line:90%
<i>I have also heard about your father.</i>

00:00:54.980 --> 00:00:58.024 line:90%
<i>How could a mere court lady</i>
<i>refuse an order?</i>

00:00:59.401 --> 00:01:01.695 line:90%
<i>Royal Noble Consort Sukbin Choi</i>
<i>forced her to do it.</i>

00:01:07.534 --> 00:01:10.704 line:90%
Your father saved your mother
by marrying her.

00:01:10.787 --> 00:01:13.540 line:90%
So do not hate your mother or father
too deeply!

00:01:15.208 --> 00:01:19.337 line:90%
Do not let the spirit of the Crown Prince
use that hatred!

00:01:20.589 --> 00:01:21.673 line:90%
<i>Princess!</i>

00:01:23.383 --> 00:01:24.426 line:90%
<i>Princess!</i>

00:01:25.260 --> 00:01:26.136 line:90%
<i>Princess.</i>

00:01:27.178 --> 00:01:28.680 line:90%
What are you looking at?

00:01:31.349 --> 00:01:34.436 line:90%
Are these yellow flowers
from the ginger tree?

00:01:34.519 --> 00:01:35.812 line:90%
Yes, they are.

00:01:36.730 --> 00:01:39.065 line:90%
There are many in my hometown.

00:01:39.858 --> 00:01:44.529 line:90%
I told His Majesty of it,
and he chose it as your childhood name.

00:01:47.282 --> 00:01:49.910 line:90%
Do you miss your hometown, Mother?

00:01:49.993 --> 00:01:51.536 line:90%
No.

00:01:52.871 --> 00:01:54.664 line:90%
I have no fond memories there.

00:01:55.373 --> 00:01:57.584 line:90%
My father died young,

00:01:58.084 --> 00:02:00.045 line:90%
and my mother was always ill.

00:02:03.214 --> 00:02:04.591 line:90%
Then, Mother,

00:02:05.258 --> 00:02:07.969 line:90%
be my daughter in the next life.

00:02:08.929 --> 00:02:10.597 line:90%
I will keep you safe.

00:02:16.269 --> 00:02:18.563 line:90%
That is a wonderful idea.

00:02:38.833 --> 00:02:39.834 line:90%
What in the world…

00:02:41.544 --> 00:02:42.754 line:90%
-Your leg…
-Your Highness!

00:02:44.089 --> 00:02:45.048 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:02:45.131 --> 00:02:46.591 line:90%
-Are you all right?
-Anyone there?

00:02:46.675 --> 00:02:48.426 line:90%
-Are you all right?
-Is anyone there?

00:02:48.510 --> 00:02:49.552 line:90%
We need to press on it!

00:02:49.636 --> 00:02:52.347 line:90%
-Your Highness, are you all right?
-Check outside.

00:02:52.847 --> 00:02:54.641 line:90%
-Now!
-Yes, Your Majesty.

00:02:55.517 --> 00:02:58.436 line:90%
Where are you going, Your Highness?

00:03:00.105 --> 00:03:00.939 line:90%
Sir.

00:03:07.404 --> 00:03:08.321 line:90%
What's the matter?

00:03:19.874 --> 00:03:21.209 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:03:23.628 --> 00:03:25.964 line:90%
Can you see now? How…

00:03:26.047 --> 00:03:27.465 line:90%
Let us stop the bleeding first.

00:03:33.972 --> 00:03:34.973 line:90%
That was close.

00:03:35.056 --> 00:03:38.685 line:90%
It was fortunate that the spirit
of the Crown Prince fled when you awoke.

00:03:40.562 --> 00:03:42.272 line:90%
I was a fool.

00:03:43.023 --> 00:03:44.649 line:90%
I let the spirit

00:03:45.150 --> 00:03:46.818 line:90%
use my body

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:48.611 line:90%
to pass the ward.

00:03:48.695 --> 00:03:50.530 line:90%
Let us go to the physician first.

00:03:54.117 --> 00:03:55.076 line:90%
Before that,

00:03:56.911 --> 00:03:58.830 line:90%
where is my mother?

00:04:00.665 --> 00:04:02.000 line:90%
I wish to see her.

00:04:02.834 --> 00:04:05.378 line:90%
I must tell her
that I will release her resentment

00:04:05.462 --> 00:04:10.050 line:90%
so she may pass on to the afterlife
without worry.

00:04:11.551 --> 00:04:12.886 line:90%
That will not be possible.

00:04:14.804 --> 00:04:16.514 line:90%
-It is possible.
-No, it is not.

00:04:17.265 --> 00:04:19.309 line:90%
Her soul was taken by a gwi-mae.

00:04:21.186 --> 00:04:22.103 line:90%
What?

00:04:23.730 --> 00:04:28.777 line:90%
-What does that--
-Your mother's soul has perished.

00:04:43.416 --> 00:04:45.126 line:90%
Go to Saeng-gang!

00:04:45.627 --> 00:04:46.878 line:90%
I will be fine,

00:04:47.462 --> 00:04:51.174 line:90%
so please protect my daughter, Saeng-gang!

00:04:58.014 --> 00:04:59.307 line:90%
I am sorry.

00:06:17.051 --> 00:06:21.973 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:06:23.391 --> 00:06:25.894 line:90%
The Princess came to see me last night.

00:06:27.103 --> 00:06:28.771 line:90%
The eunuchs told me

00:06:29.522 --> 00:06:31.733 line:90%
that she was acting strangely.

00:06:31.816 --> 00:06:32.984 line:90%
It is nothing.

00:06:33.067 --> 00:06:34.944 line:90%
There is no need for concern.

00:06:36.237 --> 00:06:39.324 line:90%
More importantly,
I must go outside the palace.

00:06:39.407 --> 00:06:42.285 line:90%
-For the Crown Prince's soul to pass--
-There is no need.

00:06:42.368 --> 00:06:46.247 line:90%
Do not send it to the afterlife.
Destroy it.

00:06:49.459 --> 00:06:51.169 line:90%
Do you understand what it means

00:06:52.587 --> 00:06:54.088 line:90%
to destroy a soul?

00:06:54.172 --> 00:06:55.131 line:90%
It matters not.

00:06:55.215 --> 00:06:58.176 line:90%
In any case, you cannot leave.

00:06:59.093 --> 00:07:01.763 line:90%
-Leave outside matters to the Princess.
-No.

00:07:01.846 --> 00:07:04.307 line:90%
I will tell the Princess
to step away from this matter.

00:07:04.390 --> 00:07:05.767 line:90%
It is too dangerous.

00:07:07.143 --> 00:07:09.020 line:90%
You said it was nothing.

00:07:15.401 --> 00:07:18.488 line:90%
So something has happened to the Princess.

00:07:18.988 --> 00:07:20.323 line:90%
And…

00:07:23.743 --> 00:07:25.995 line:90%
something has happened to you as well.

00:07:35.672 --> 00:07:38.800 line:90%
I summoned the Princess
because she can hear spirits.

00:07:39.467 --> 00:07:41.302 line:90%
She may be of use,

00:07:41.803 --> 00:07:43.221 line:90%
so work with her.

00:07:43.304 --> 00:07:45.932 line:90%
I clearly told you
the Princess was in danger.

00:07:46.015 --> 00:07:49.060 line:90%
It is not your place
to concern yourself with her safety.

00:07:49.143 --> 00:07:53.606 line:90%
Or have you forgotten your lowly status
and dared to set your heart on her?

00:07:56.234 --> 00:07:57.443 line:90%
Of course not.

00:07:59.529 --> 00:08:01.281 line:90%
I only mean to stop her

00:08:01.990 --> 00:08:03.324 line:90%
because she is in the way.

00:08:04.993 --> 00:08:07.829 line:90%
As she gets closer to the truth
about the Crown Prince's spirit,

00:08:08.705 --> 00:08:11.541 line:90%
she learns of Your Majesty
and the royal family's shame.

00:08:12.208 --> 00:08:14.752 line:90%
And it is becoming harder for her to bear.

00:08:38.359 --> 00:08:40.236 line:90%
Why are you still here?

00:08:42.780 --> 00:08:44.782 line:90%
In case you get possessed again.

00:08:53.416 --> 00:08:54.876 line:90%
Tell me now.

00:08:55.460 --> 00:08:58.087 line:90%
How did you regain your sight?

00:09:00.423 --> 00:09:01.924 line:90%
I gained the eyes of a gwi-mae.

00:09:02.008 --> 00:09:03.134 line:90%
The eyes of a gwi-mae?

00:09:03.217 --> 00:09:05.595 line:90%
What happens to you, then?

00:09:07.096 --> 00:09:10.099 line:90%
Well, do not concern yourself with that.
Just keep this well.

00:09:10.850 --> 00:09:12.518 line:90%
Do not lose it.

00:09:13.603 --> 00:09:16.773 line:90%
Do not concern yourself with the spirit
of the Crown Prince as well.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:18.941 line:90%
Now that I have my sight back,

00:09:19.901 --> 00:09:21.778 line:90%
I will deal with spirits alone.

00:09:21.861 --> 00:09:23.029 line:90%
Why all of a sudden--

00:09:23.112 --> 00:09:24.530 line:90%
Because you get in the way.

00:09:27.617 --> 00:09:30.495 line:90%
The spirit of the Crown Prince
might take over your body again.

00:09:33.206 --> 00:09:36.042 line:90%
I am at my wit's end
cleaning up after you.

00:09:36.125 --> 00:09:37.168 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:09:49.931 --> 00:09:51.641 line:90%
Is this because of my mother?

00:09:53.559 --> 00:09:54.936 line:90%
If that is the reason…

00:09:57.271 --> 00:09:58.606 line:90%
do not concern yourself.

00:09:59.941 --> 00:10:02.235 line:90%
She met her end trying to save me,

00:10:02.735 --> 00:10:04.487 line:90%
so you have nothing to be sorry for.

00:10:05.613 --> 00:10:07.407 line:90%
It is not your fault.

00:10:09.909 --> 00:10:11.994 line:90%
-Do you hear me?
-It is my fault.

00:10:14.914 --> 00:10:16.124 line:90%
Once before…

00:10:18.418 --> 00:10:21.671 line:90%
a gwi-mae was after my Yin energy,
and I let it devour a soul.

00:10:23.506 --> 00:10:26.092 line:90%
So you should stay away from me.

00:10:27.093 --> 00:10:30.388 line:90%
You never know what might happen
if you stay with a cursed man like me.

00:11:02.795 --> 00:11:04.380 line:90%
<i>I will not lose anyone</i>

00:11:05.548 --> 00:11:07.925 line:90%
<i>because of me again.</i>

00:11:13.514 --> 00:11:16.100 line:90%
Did you bring those wards
from your residence?

00:11:18.269 --> 00:11:19.437 line:90%
That is quite a lot.

00:11:20.104 --> 00:11:21.522 line:90%
You may all leave.

00:11:22.106 --> 00:11:23.566 line:90%
-Yes.
-Yes.

00:11:28.613 --> 00:11:31.991 line:90%
Where did you go last night?

00:11:33.367 --> 00:11:34.702 line:90%
Come here.

00:11:35.453 --> 00:11:36.412 line:90%
Come now.

00:11:37.705 --> 00:11:39.624 line:90%
Come, dear.

00:11:45.087 --> 00:11:50.468 line:90%
You must be
my dearest granddaughter again.

00:11:50.551 --> 00:11:51.511 line:90%
And

00:11:52.053 --> 00:11:54.347 line:90%
let us keep the secret of 30 years ago

00:11:54.847 --> 00:11:57.934 line:90%
and protect our family together.

00:12:01.103 --> 00:12:04.398 line:90%
Someone has already begun to notice.

00:12:06.150 --> 00:12:07.401 line:90%
Your Highness.

00:12:07.485 --> 00:12:10.488 line:90%
The Queen Dowager urgently requests
your presence at her residence.

00:12:13.449 --> 00:12:15.660 line:90%
His Majesty the King has arrived.

00:12:40.893 --> 00:12:42.103 line:90%
You may all be seated.

00:12:48.901 --> 00:12:51.112 line:90%
You even summoned the royal relatives.

00:12:51.195 --> 00:12:53.614 line:90%
What did you wish to see me about
so urgently?

00:12:54.115 --> 00:12:56.867 line:90%
I have no leisure to enjoy refreshments.

00:12:56.951 --> 00:12:58.953 line:90%
Thirty years ago,

00:13:00.538 --> 00:13:04.166 line:90%
when the late King's sons
met their untimely deaths,

00:13:05.001 --> 00:13:09.630 line:90%
you were the only one to survive. Why?

00:13:16.387 --> 00:13:18.139 line:90%
Has my survival

00:13:19.807 --> 00:13:23.227 line:90%
displeased you all this time, Mother?

00:13:23.311 --> 00:13:29.191 line:90%
I ask how you escaped
the curse of the pond spirit.

00:13:29.275 --> 00:13:32.695 line:90%
At the time, I took refuge in the temple
of a monk known for exorcisms.

00:13:32.778 --> 00:13:35.698 line:90%
-You already knew, did you not?
-No!

00:13:36.490 --> 00:13:38.576 line:90%
There was no need.

00:13:39.076 --> 00:13:41.537 line:90%
Because the pond spirit
never existed to begin with.

00:13:42.997 --> 00:13:47.043 line:90%
The deaths of the Princes 30 years ago
were not the work of the pond spirit.

00:13:47.126 --> 00:13:48.836 line:90%
This was clearly

00:13:49.462 --> 00:13:52.465 line:90%
poisoning by human hands.

00:13:52.548 --> 00:13:54.717 line:90%
Bring him in!

00:14:07.688 --> 00:14:11.108 line:90%
Prince Inha collapsed
as soon as he entered the palace.

00:14:11.609 --> 00:14:14.862 line:90%
And something was found in his quarters.

00:14:19.158 --> 00:14:21.994 line:90%
The refreshment box Prince Inha ate from.

00:14:22.662 --> 00:14:24.330 line:90%
And there is another.

00:14:25.247 --> 00:14:27.792 line:90%
The one the Princess gave me.

00:14:28.793 --> 00:14:33.297 line:90%
I heard her mother died after eating
from that lotus-patterned box as well.

00:14:33.798 --> 00:14:38.177 line:90%
This clearly proves the Princes
were not killed by the pond spirit

00:14:38.260 --> 00:14:41.389 line:90%
but were poisoned.

00:14:42.431 --> 00:14:44.475 line:90%
What do you think, Your Majesty?

00:14:47.520 --> 00:14:49.021 line:90%
Are you saying…

00:14:51.565 --> 00:14:55.277 line:90%
that I killed my own brothers?

00:14:55.361 --> 00:15:00.449 line:90%
When everyone else is killed,
the sole survivor is the culprit.

00:15:00.950 --> 00:15:02.952 line:90%
I speak of Your Majesty,

00:15:03.035 --> 00:15:06.664 line:90%
who could never have risen
to the throne otherwise.

00:15:07.164 --> 00:15:09.667 line:90%
What you just said…

00:15:12.586 --> 00:15:15.131 line:90%
Can you bear what you have said?

00:15:34.650 --> 00:15:36.318 line:90%
What do you think you are doing?

00:15:42.366 --> 00:15:43.576 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:16:53.521 --> 00:16:55.105 line:90%
You said it was poison.

00:16:55.189 --> 00:16:57.650 line:90%
We shall see in time.

00:17:01.028 --> 00:17:01.987 line:90%
Oh, right.

00:17:03.823 --> 00:17:06.242 line:90%
-Chief Eunuch Kim.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

00:17:08.702 --> 00:17:12.540 line:90%
-Take Prince Inha outside the palace now.
-Take him outside the palace?

00:17:14.875 --> 00:17:16.710 line:90%
There is something I wish to see.

00:17:19.338 --> 00:17:20.881 line:90%
Stop!

00:17:29.265 --> 00:17:30.140 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:17:31.100 --> 00:17:34.979 line:90%
Prince Inha awoke
the moment he left the palace.

00:17:35.062 --> 00:17:35.938 line:90%
What?

00:17:36.438 --> 00:17:39.024 line:90%
And he asked that a message be delivered.

00:17:39.108 --> 00:17:41.735 line:90%
What? What did he say?

00:17:42.653 --> 00:17:44.530 line:90%
A spirit tried to kill him.

00:17:45.656 --> 00:17:48.325 line:90%
He said that it would wipe out
the royal bloodline.

00:17:49.034 --> 00:17:50.744 line:90%
That cannot be.

00:17:50.828 --> 00:17:53.080 line:90%
He was clearly poisoned.

00:17:53.163 --> 00:17:54.206 line:90%
Poisoned?

00:17:54.290 --> 00:17:56.959 line:90%
How can you say such a ridiculous thing?

00:17:57.459 --> 00:18:03.173 line:90%
Are you saying I killed my own sons
with my own hands?

00:18:06.635 --> 00:18:08.971 line:90%
They were all killed by the pond spirit.

00:18:10.139 --> 00:18:13.851 line:90%
I speak of the Most Favored Lady
of the Court you killed.

00:18:14.351 --> 00:18:15.477 line:90%
No.

00:18:17.271 --> 00:18:19.231 line:90%
I hesitated because you were unwell.

00:18:19.315 --> 00:18:22.067 line:90%
But I have no choice now.

00:18:22.151 --> 00:18:28.073 line:90%
You brutally killed that pregnant lady
and cut off the royal bloodline.

00:18:28.157 --> 00:18:32.995 line:90%
You even dared brand me,
the King of this land, a murderer!

00:18:33.078 --> 00:18:35.623 line:90%
I will tolerate this no longer!

00:18:38.876 --> 00:18:40.586 line:90%
Leave the palace.

00:18:41.879 --> 00:18:42.963 line:90%
At once.

00:19:00.230 --> 00:19:02.942 line:90%
How dare you!

00:19:03.692 --> 00:19:05.861 line:90%
I already know the truth!

00:19:05.945 --> 00:19:09.573 line:90%
This was all your doing! I know it all!

00:19:10.157 --> 00:19:11.951 line:90%
I know everything!

00:19:12.451 --> 00:19:14.203 line:90%
I know it all, you wretch!

00:19:20.250 --> 00:19:21.919 line:90%
No, you are wrong.

00:19:23.587 --> 00:19:25.047 line:90%
It was you.

00:19:26.256 --> 00:19:29.468 line:90%
It was you who started

00:19:30.719 --> 00:19:32.054 line:90%
all this curse and tragedy.

00:19:32.137 --> 00:19:33.973 line:90%
You are the one

00:19:34.723 --> 00:19:37.893 line:90%
who dragged me into this hell.

00:19:37.977 --> 00:19:40.104 line:90%
All because of you.

00:19:41.981 --> 00:19:44.775 line:90%
It is time you accept it.

00:19:45.401 --> 00:19:46.443 line:90%
This is…

00:19:50.572 --> 00:19:52.533 line:90%
your retribution.

00:19:54.034 --> 00:19:55.327 line:90%
Mother.

00:20:13.721 --> 00:20:16.890 line:90%
I will never leave.

00:20:18.225 --> 00:20:21.770 line:90%
This palace belongs to me!

00:20:21.854 --> 00:20:24.982 line:90%
I will not leave, even in death!

00:20:25.065 --> 00:20:27.693 line:90%
I will never leave!

00:20:27.776 --> 00:20:31.030 line:90%
This palace is mine!

00:20:31.113 --> 00:20:34.867 line:90%
-Your Majesty, are you all right?
-It is mine!

00:20:34.950 --> 00:20:35.951 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:20:37.911 --> 00:20:39.163 line:90%
Father!

00:20:45.586 --> 00:20:46.754 line:90%
Let us leave.

00:20:55.679 --> 00:20:57.890 line:90%
Did you even use
the spirit of the Crown Prince?

00:20:58.599 --> 00:21:01.477 line:90%
Knowing the spirit would harm him,
you took Prince Inha in.

00:21:02.144 --> 00:21:03.812 line:90%
How could you…

00:21:03.896 --> 00:21:05.773 line:90%
You are the one who is out of your mind.

00:21:06.607 --> 00:21:08.984 line:90%
And who are you today?

00:21:10.903 --> 00:21:12.362 line:90%
Are you truly the Princess?

00:21:14.823 --> 00:21:17.785 line:90%
Do not appear before me
until the pond spirit is destroyed.

00:21:17.868 --> 00:21:19.745 line:90%
I cannot trust you.

00:21:19.828 --> 00:21:22.790 line:90%
I cannot trust you either, Father.

00:21:26.877 --> 00:21:29.963 line:90%
Why did your first
and second sons die, Father?

00:21:31.173 --> 00:21:32.549 line:90%
Like your third son,

00:21:33.759 --> 00:21:35.427 line:90%
did you poison them as well?

00:21:37.221 --> 00:21:39.056 line:90%
The consequences of that sin

00:21:40.641 --> 00:21:42.768 line:90%
will surely come upon you.

00:21:48.232 --> 00:21:49.149 line:90%
Very well.

00:21:51.777 --> 00:21:52.986 line:90%
I will be waiting.

00:22:01.954 --> 00:22:07.167 line:90%
I must kill the King.

00:22:07.668 --> 00:22:09.128 line:90%
The King…

00:22:10.295 --> 00:22:14.550 line:90%
I must kill the King.

00:22:16.844 --> 00:22:18.303 line:90%
You may enter.

00:22:31.692 --> 00:22:34.361 line:90%
<i>Are you saying the pestilence</i>
<i>is near the capital?</i>

00:22:34.444 --> 00:22:35.946 line:90%
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

00:22:36.029 --> 00:22:37.906 line:90%
All gates to the capital are closed,

00:22:37.990 --> 00:22:40.367 line:90%
and the people are barred
from entering or leaving.

00:22:42.035 --> 00:22:44.830 line:90%
Jeonuigam, Hyeminseo, and Hwalinseo.

00:22:44.913 --> 00:22:48.834 line:90%
Find a way to stop the pestilence
and report to me.

00:22:48.917 --> 00:22:52.546 line:90%
And the Ministry of Taxation.
Release the stored grain--

00:22:53.463 --> 00:22:54.631 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:23:01.513 --> 00:23:02.431 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:23:03.473 --> 00:23:05.100 line:90%
The pestilence has reached you.

00:23:05.726 --> 00:23:08.228 line:90%
-I will summon the royal physician.
-No.

00:23:12.357 --> 00:23:13.233 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:23:15.527 --> 00:23:17.571 line:90%
Gu-cheon. Bring him here.

00:23:18.071 --> 00:23:18.989 line:90%
Now.

00:23:24.453 --> 00:23:25.579 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:23:27.122 --> 00:23:28.916 line:90%
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

00:23:29.416 --> 00:23:30.709 line:90%
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

00:23:30.792 --> 00:23:31.919 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:23:33.128 --> 00:23:34.963 line:90%
Take a good look at me.

00:23:42.888 --> 00:23:44.514 line:90%
What do you see?

00:23:46.558 --> 00:23:49.811 line:90%
Something different from the spirits
I usually see in the palace.

00:23:49.895 --> 00:23:53.649 line:90%
-I see the people wailing.
-My lord.

00:23:54.316 --> 00:23:56.777 line:90%
-Please help us.
-Spots are all over their bodies…

00:23:56.860 --> 00:24:00.656 line:90%
-There is a child of Prince Yeongan's age.
-My lord, please help us.

00:24:00.739 --> 00:24:03.367 line:90%
She is holding onto Your Majesty's robe.

00:24:06.328 --> 00:24:07.996 line:90%
They are the people you killed…

00:24:10.165 --> 00:24:12.334 line:90%
in the village affected by the pestilence.

00:24:13.043 --> 00:24:17.547 line:90%
Are you saying they came to the palace
with resentment against me?

00:24:18.048 --> 00:24:19.758 line:90%
Won-gwi are quite simple.

00:24:19.841 --> 00:24:23.845 line:90%
If they bore resentment, they would seek
the soldiers who killed them.

00:24:26.139 --> 00:24:28.767 line:90%
Yet they came for Your Majesty,
who gave the order.

00:24:29.810 --> 00:24:31.895 line:90%
As though someone guided them here.

00:24:34.022 --> 00:24:36.817 line:90%
Then the one who brought them
into the palace must be…

00:24:43.240 --> 00:24:44.741 line:90%
The spirit of the Crown Prince.

00:24:56.378 --> 00:24:59.673 line:90%
Then go and see it done.

00:25:02.301 --> 00:25:04.303 line:90%
Then what will you do with them?

00:25:05.429 --> 00:25:07.931 line:90%
If you leave them be,
Your Majesty will be in danger.

00:25:08.515 --> 00:25:09.933 line:90%
An appeasement rite.

00:25:11.101 --> 00:25:13.103 line:90%
I will perform the rite tomorrow night

00:25:13.979 --> 00:25:16.356 line:90%
to drive out the pestilent-gwis.

00:25:16.440 --> 00:25:17.858 line:90%
Drive them out?

00:25:19.234 --> 00:25:24.281 line:90%
That mindset will not do.
The rite appeases the wronged souls.

00:25:24.364 --> 00:25:29.369 line:90%
-Such an approach will only fail.
-Just focus on the Crown Prince's spirit.

00:25:30.954 --> 00:25:33.582 line:90%
The time we agreed upon is near.

00:26:22.422 --> 00:26:23.715 line:90%
What are you doing?

00:26:24.216 --> 00:26:25.300 line:90%
It is calling

00:26:26.051 --> 00:26:27.135 line:90%
me.

00:26:30.555 --> 00:26:31.515 line:90%
Who?

00:26:35.352 --> 00:26:36.228 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:26:38.355 --> 00:26:39.523 line:90%
It is nothing.

00:26:41.942 --> 00:26:42.984 line:90%
Tell me.

00:26:43.068 --> 00:26:46.113 line:90%
Has your condition worsened
since you gained the eyes of gwi-mae?

00:26:46.196 --> 00:26:48.073 line:90%
More importantly, why are you here?

00:26:49.116 --> 00:26:51.493 line:90%
I told you
I would handle the spirit alone.

00:26:55.872 --> 00:26:57.332 line:90%
Must you be like this?

00:26:59.418 --> 00:27:04.089 line:90%
I told you my mother's soul perished
because of me being possessed, not you.

00:27:10.387 --> 00:27:12.889 line:90%
I know this is all out of concern for me.

00:27:14.099 --> 00:27:16.226 line:90%
What has happened

00:27:17.102 --> 00:27:18.854 line:90%
and what will happen

00:27:19.855 --> 00:27:21.565 line:90%
are all mine to bear.

00:27:22.065 --> 00:27:23.483 line:90%
Not yours.

00:27:30.365 --> 00:27:32.868 line:90%
<i>The Crown Prince's spirit</i>
<i>failed to reach the King.</i>

00:27:34.327 --> 00:27:36.913 line:90%
<i>Now it is drawing in the pestilent-gwis.</i>

00:27:36.997 --> 00:27:39.499 line:90%
I will draw them all in.

00:27:39.583 --> 00:27:41.585 line:90%
<i>The spirit of the Crown Prince</i>

00:27:42.752 --> 00:27:44.713 line:90%
<i>will surely try to kill the King.</i>

00:27:46.965 --> 00:27:48.425 line:90%
<i>Draw them in…</i>

00:27:50.093 --> 00:27:52.554 line:90%
<i>I could not even protect</i>
<i>your mother's soul.</i>

00:27:54.222 --> 00:27:56.558 line:90%
So I cannot let your father die as well.

00:28:02.189 --> 00:28:04.858 line:90%
I should send you
out of the palace at once,

00:28:05.775 --> 00:28:07.569 line:90%
but I cannot for now.

00:28:08.778 --> 00:28:10.572 line:90%
You are the only one I can rely on.

00:28:14.326 --> 00:28:16.620 line:90%
Let us wait until sunrise

00:28:17.496 --> 00:28:19.122 line:90%
so I can replenish my Yang energy.

00:28:34.221 --> 00:28:36.515 line:90%
I will share my Yang energy with you.

00:29:06.753 --> 00:29:09.756 line:90%
<i>I will find out what the pestilent-gwis</i>
<i>will be used for.</i>

00:29:10.632 --> 00:29:13.677 line:90%
<i>In the meantime,</i>
<i>you should buy me some time.</i>

00:29:15.804 --> 00:29:17.639 line:90%
<i>Write the protective sutra,</i>

00:29:17.722 --> 00:29:20.600 line:90%
<i>coat it with chicken blood,</i>
<i>and put it in the King's bedchamber.</i>

00:29:23.144 --> 00:29:26.481 line:90%
<i>That way, the Crown Prince</i>
<i>will not be able to approach easily.</i>

00:29:29.067 --> 00:29:32.737 line:90%
<i>The King must be protected</i>
<i>until the appeasement rite.</i>

00:29:39.411 --> 00:29:40.745 line:90%
What are you doing?

00:29:40.829 --> 00:29:43.248 line:90%
From now on,
do not let anyone enter this chamber.

00:30:00.599 --> 00:30:02.017 line:90%
I asked you what you are doing.

00:30:02.100 --> 00:30:04.311 line:90%
-Why are you here?
-I did not wish to come either.

00:30:04.394 --> 00:30:08.315 line:90%
But I was told I must protect you
until the appeasement rite.

00:30:11.484 --> 00:30:13.695 line:90%
So that is what Gu-cheon said.

00:30:18.533 --> 00:30:21.077 line:90%
<i>I must tell you something, Your Majesty.</i>

00:30:22.704 --> 00:30:23.663 line:90%
What is the matter?

00:30:25.498 --> 00:30:29.711 line:90%
Something is here,
but not a pestilent-gwi.

00:30:30.503 --> 00:30:31.546 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:30:32.589 --> 00:30:33.548 line:90%
Behind you, Father…

00:30:36.301 --> 00:30:38.219 line:90%
I must tell you about the Crown Prince.

00:30:38.803 --> 00:30:39.679 line:90%
Stop there.

00:30:39.763 --> 00:30:42.724 line:90%
Please hear me out, Your Majesty.

00:30:45.769 --> 00:30:48.605 line:90%
-He is about to speak of the Crown Prince.
-Please…

00:30:48.688 --> 00:30:50.649 line:90%
No. Do not listen to him.

00:30:50.732 --> 00:30:53.735 line:90%
-Please hear me out.
-What else are you trying to hide?

00:30:54.527 --> 00:30:57.030 line:90%
-Leave at once. Now!
-No.

00:30:57.656 --> 00:31:01.951 line:90%
-Say it yourself. You cannot avoid it now.
-That is enough, Saeng-gang!

00:31:02.035 --> 00:31:04.996 line:90%
I must hear that spirit's plea.

00:31:05.080 --> 00:31:06.873 line:90%
-Please…
-I must know what it has to say.

00:31:09.209 --> 00:31:11.628 line:90%
Do not come closer. Do not listen to it.

00:31:11.711 --> 00:31:13.838 line:90%
Do not try to find out anything more!

00:31:13.922 --> 00:31:14.756 line:90%
Leave at once!

00:31:14.839 --> 00:31:17.384 line:90%
-I said leave at once!
-Father!

00:31:47.247 --> 00:31:48.498 line:90%
Who is he?

00:31:50.041 --> 00:31:53.503 line:90%
Did you kill him as well, Father?

00:31:55.922 --> 00:31:56.881 line:90%
Yes, I did.

00:31:59.509 --> 00:32:01.428 line:90%
Why did you kill him?

00:32:04.889 --> 00:32:06.349 line:90%
He…

00:32:12.480 --> 00:32:14.649 line:90%
He was about to speak of…

00:32:19.821 --> 00:32:21.531 line:90%
what the Crown Prince had done.

00:32:33.293 --> 00:32:34.335 line:90%
I see.

00:32:38.715 --> 00:32:40.675 line:90%
This palace has always been

00:32:41.551 --> 00:32:43.136 line:90%
quite an interesting place.

00:32:45.346 --> 00:32:46.639 line:90%
Is that not so?

00:32:55.190 --> 00:32:56.608 line:90%
Are you saying

00:32:57.567 --> 00:33:00.361 line:90%
the Crown Prince could hear the spirits
as well?

00:33:17.921 --> 00:33:19.214 line:90%
Tell me

00:33:19.714 --> 00:33:22.509 line:90%
how I became King.

00:33:29.349 --> 00:33:35.021 line:90%
-The late King's Princes died one by one--
-And what about the Princes?

00:33:37.440 --> 00:33:39.025 line:90%
Tell me how they died.

00:33:42.612 --> 00:33:44.405 line:90%
I heard it was the pond spirit's curse.

00:33:47.784 --> 00:33:49.494 line:90%
Tell me the truth.

00:33:51.079 --> 00:33:52.997 line:90%
I do not understand what you mean…

00:33:53.081 --> 00:33:56.793 line:90%
In my mother's bloodline,

00:33:56.876 --> 00:34:01.798 line:90%
some children are born with a cursed gift
passed down through generations.

00:34:01.881 --> 00:34:03.883 line:90%
You are one of them.

00:34:05.593 --> 00:34:10.723 line:90%
Since you can hear the spirits,
you must have known long ago

00:34:10.807 --> 00:34:13.059 line:90%
that the pond spirit was never real.

00:34:13.142 --> 00:34:16.271 line:90%
And that it was not a spirit
that killed the late King's Princes…

00:34:19.983 --> 00:34:22.110 line:90%
but a human.

00:34:26.281 --> 00:34:27.282 line:90%
Father!

00:34:27.365 --> 00:34:28.366 line:90%
And yet

00:34:28.867 --> 00:34:32.412 line:90%
my first and second sons died.

00:34:32.912 --> 00:34:36.457 line:90%
Even though the pond spirit
was never real.

00:34:37.125 --> 00:34:40.753 line:90%
They coughed up black blood
as my brothers did.

00:34:42.589 --> 00:34:43.631 line:90%
You

00:34:45.341 --> 00:34:49.095 line:90%
must have heard of the secret
from 30 years ago

00:34:49.846 --> 00:34:51.723 line:90%
and recreated it.

00:35:02.150 --> 00:35:04.944 line:90%
Did you think I would spare you?

00:35:19.834 --> 00:35:20.835 line:90%
Did you truly…

00:35:23.671 --> 00:35:25.757 line:90%
put poison in the tea?

00:35:32.847 --> 00:35:34.515 line:90%
How could a father

00:35:35.016 --> 00:35:37.894 line:90%
kill his own child with his own hands?

00:35:37.977 --> 00:35:41.314 line:90%
You should not become King
and rule the people.

00:35:41.814 --> 00:35:43.983 line:90%
You must never become King.

00:35:44.067 --> 00:35:45.151 line:90%
Why?

00:35:46.402 --> 00:35:49.238 line:90%
You became King that way, so why?

00:35:49.948 --> 00:35:52.951 line:90%
Why can I not?

00:36:11.052 --> 00:36:13.972 line:90%
One man who killed his brothers
to become King is enough.

00:36:15.223 --> 00:36:17.517 line:90%
And that man is me.

00:36:20.645 --> 00:36:21.813 line:90%
You, too…

00:36:24.691 --> 00:36:27.568 line:90%
will be said to have died
from the curse of the pond spirit.

00:36:29.696 --> 00:36:31.739 line:90%
Yes, do as you wish.

00:36:50.174 --> 00:36:53.261 line:90%
Since you are the pond spirit,

00:36:54.804 --> 00:36:58.182 line:90%
it is only fitting
that a spirit kill me as well.

00:37:03.771 --> 00:37:05.523 line:90%
And I will die…

00:37:09.944 --> 00:37:14.032 line:90%
and become the true pond spirit for you.

00:37:26.127 --> 00:37:28.337 line:90%
Father!

00:37:33.509 --> 00:37:37.221 line:90%
As the curse said 30 years ago…

00:37:41.392 --> 00:37:46.814 line:90%
I will cut off the royal bloodline.

00:37:50.068 --> 00:37:54.572 line:90%
If I cannot become King…

00:38:03.414 --> 00:38:04.457 line:90%
Father.

00:38:15.218 --> 00:38:16.219 line:90%
Father.

00:38:16.719 --> 00:38:17.720 line:90%
Father!

00:38:21.766 --> 00:38:26.687 line:90%
<i>You cannot be King either, Father.</i>

00:38:57.885 --> 00:39:02.557 line:90%
May peace and prosperity
fill this household!

00:39:02.640 --> 00:39:06.936 line:90%
With one heart,
we offer our solemn prayers!

00:39:07.520 --> 00:39:11.941 line:90%
Your Highness, the Crown Prince,
guardian deity of the palace!

00:39:12.024 --> 00:39:14.318 line:90%
Accept this humble offering

00:39:14.402 --> 00:39:18.990 line:90%
and drive the pestilent-gwis
out of the palace!

00:39:29.876 --> 00:39:32.128 line:90%
Is he devouring human souls
like a gwi-mae?

00:39:32.712 --> 00:39:34.505 line:90%
Stop it!

00:40:23.930 --> 00:40:24.931 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:40:30.394 --> 00:40:31.812 line:90%
Is His Majesty…

00:40:34.398 --> 00:40:35.691 line:90%
dead?

00:40:36.192 --> 00:40:37.360 line:90%
Father.

00:40:37.860 --> 00:40:38.903 line:90%
Father!

00:40:50.414 --> 00:40:51.707 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:44:18.456 --> 00:44:21.667 line:90%
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang